basic_information
Mail
Department
grade
id
name
sex
ID_number
Birth_year
Birth_month
Birthday
Mail
Tel
PK
CREATE TABLE basic_information
(department nvarchar(20),
grade nvarchar(20),
id1 nvarchar(20),
name nvarchar(50),
sex nvarchar(200),
id_number nvarchar(20),
birth_year nvarchar(20),
birth_month nvarchar(20),
birthday nvarchar(20),
mail nvarchar(200),
tel nvarchar(20),
Primary Key (id1))
Achievement
id
Academic_performance1
Academic_performance2
Performance1
Performance2
FK
CREATE TABLE achievement
(id1 nvarchar(20) references basic_information (id1),
academic_performance1 nvarchar(20),
academic_performance2 nvarchar(20),
performance1 nvarchar(20),
performance2 nvarchar(20),
)
Family_profile
id
Family_size
Number_of_students
Number_of_employees
Parent_Career
Income_situation
other
FK
CREATE TABLE family_profile
(id1 nvarchar(20) references basic_information (id1),
family_size nvarchar(20),
number_of_students nvarchar(20),
number_of_employees nvarchar(20),
parent_Career nvarchar(20),
income_situation nvarchar(20),
other nvarchar(20),
)
study_qualification
FK
CREATE TABLE study_qualification
(id1 nvarchar(20) references basic_information (id1),
time nvarchar(20),
unit nvarchar(20),
expertise nvarchar(20),
application_form nvarchar(20),
signature nvarchar(20),
)
create view apple
as select
department,grade,basic_information.id1,name,sex,id_number,birth_year,birth_month,birthday,mail,tel,academic_performance1,academic_performance2,performance1,performan
ce2,family_size,number_of_students,number_of_employees,parent_Career,income_situation,other,time,unit,expertise,application_form,signature
from (basic_information join achievement on basic_information.id1=achievement.id1) join family_profile on basic_information.id1=family_profile.id1 join
study_qualification on basic_information.id1=study_qualification.id1
;
